Interface DataCacheJMXInstrumentMBean

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataCacheInstrument
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataCacheJMXInstrument
    public interface DataCacheJMXInstrumentMBean
extends DataCacheInstrument
    Simple MBean interface for providing instrumented data cache metrics and operations. Note: Simple MBeans require an MBean interface matching the supplied implementation class.
